# ConfigLoaderSystem  (sbx)

## Purpose
One-shot initialization system for SandboxApp. On the first frame, reads
`Assets/App/Config.json` and creates SandboxConfigSingletonComponent containing every UUID the
showcase needs: two fonts, the sprite, textured-quad and animated-character textures, the main UI layout, the UI
element ids the interaction systems target (toggle button, toggle panel, status text, close
button, close target), the three button textures swapped on interaction (default / hover /
pressed), the sound/music clips, and the 3D model for the forthcoming 3D scene. No-op on all
subsequent frames (presence check guards early exit).

## Input Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SandboxConfigSingletonComponent | read | Presence-check only; if present, system exits immediately |

## Output Components
| Component | Access | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| SandboxConfigSingletonComponent | add (deferred) | Created once from Assets/App/Config.json |
